article_title: Crews battle grass fire in Reno County
article_text:
MGN Online

Crews from two fire districts are dealing with a grass fire in Reno County.

The fire is currently burning near US Highway 50 and Andre Road. Reno County dispatchers says crews are monitoring the fire and working to contain it.

There are no reports of any damage to buildings and no injuries have been reported.
